{"article_id":"6Opn1uLPbrg5g9rT","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"NEW YORK -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Michael Bloomberg will not accept political donations","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"if he runs for president","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"and he will not take a salary","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"if he wins ,","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"according to senior aides","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"who offered new details on Saturday about the New York billionaire ' s plans","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"to navigate his wealth","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"as he marches toward a formal 2020 announcement .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"\" He has never taken a political contribution in his life .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"He is not about to start , \"","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"Bloomberg chief adviser Howard Wolfson said in an interview .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"\" He can not be bought . \"","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"One of the richest men in the world , Bloomberg is sending every indication","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"he has decided to enter the crowded Democratic presidential primary election .","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"In recent days , he has created a presidential campaign committee with the Federal Election Commission","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"and qualified for the primary ballot in at least three states .","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"Bloomberg ' s team has reserved more than $ 30 million in television ads","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"set to begin running Sunday in several primary states .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"The moves , just 10 weeks before primary voting begins in Iowa ,","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"reflects his concern","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"that the current Democratic field is not well-positioned","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"to defeat President Donald Trump next fall .","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"Bloomberg ' s wealth has already emerged as a central issue","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"as the political world awaits his formal announcement .","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"He is estimated to be one of the 10 richest people in the world .","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"His Democratic rivals pounced on news of Bloomberg ' s massive television ad buy , in addition to his decision","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"to bypass the first four states on the presidential primary calendar","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"- Iowa , New Hampshire , Nevada and South Carolina -","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"in favor of focusing on the many states","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"that hold primary contests in March .","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"\" I ' m disgusted by the idea","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"that Michael Bloomberg or any billionaire thinks","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"they can circumvent the political process","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"and spend tens of millions of dollars","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"to buy elections , \"","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"Democratic presidential contender Bernie Sanders , a Vermont senator , wrote Friday on Twitter .","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"\" If you can ' t build grassroots support for your candidacy ,","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"you have no business","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"running for president . \"","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"Another Democratic candidate , Minnesota Sen. Amy Klobuchar , swiped at Bloomberg","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"as she campaigned over the weekend in New Hampshire .","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"\" He didn ' t want to deal with all of this grassroots campaigning from the beginning ,","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"you know","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"that ' s on him .","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"I think","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"this is important , \"","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"Klobuchar said .","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"She added ,","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"\" I think","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"that you want to have a candidate for president","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"who ' s willing to go out , day after day ,","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"and talk to regular people like this . \"","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"Bloomberg ' s team insists","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"that his wealth allows him to be more responsive to the concerns of everyday people","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"because he isn ' t beholden to special interests .","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"Wolfson said","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"Bloomberg would work for only $ 1 a year as president ,","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"just as he did","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"when he was New York City mayor for more than a decade .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"Bloomberg ' s message on money is much the same one","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"employed by Trump in his 2016 campaign ,","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"although Trump ultimately accepted millions of dollars in donations .","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"Trump donates his salary each quarter to different departments of the federal government .","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"Bloomberg \" is wholly independent of special interests ,","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"will not take a dime in any contribution ,","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"and never has in any of his three races , \"","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"Wolfson said .","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"The decision","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"to refuse contributions","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"would make it impossible for Bloomberg to participate any sanctioned Democratic debates","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"should he run .","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"The rules of entry ,","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"as set by the Democratic National Committee ,","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"currently require participants to meet a polling threshold and raise donations from tens of thousands of voters .","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"Any money","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"Bloomberg raises","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"and spends on his presidential ambitions","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"will come from one place :","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"His own pocket .","depth":7}],"relations